# Bug Tracker

This folder contains defect tracking dashboards and bug management records created during QA testing activities.

## Included Documents

* Money Box Module Bug Tracker
* Website Modification Bug Tracker
* Defect Status Reports
* QA Metrics Dashboard

## Tracking Fields

* Bug ID
* Module
* Severity
* Priority
* Status
* Assigned To
* Retest Status

## Tools Used

* Microsoft Excel
* Jira
* GitHub
* Postman
* SQL Validation

